 * \page sys

\section sys System Support


The \c utilib/src/sys directory contains definitions for a variety of
support functions, including functions that are system-specific. These
functions are defined in the following header files:
  - _generic.h
  - alloc.h
  - errmsg.h
  - general.h
  - real.h
  - seconds.h
  - signalError.h
  - stdlibmpi.h
  - utilib_dll.h

*/
